Interests & Activities

Honorary General Secretary | SMU Gourmet Club NOV 2021 – NOV 2022 - Administrative duties in assisting the club, such as minutes crafting, email creation, and updating membership records. - Conduct and plan Annual Election.

Mentor | Cahaya Community AUG 2021 – PRESENT - Mentor students from primary school. - Assist in school homework.

Volunteer | SMU Rotaract Club AUG 2021 – JUNE 2022 - Participate in sessions to interact with beneficiaries. - Assist in conducting meet-up sessions.

Area Committee Secretary & Sub-comm | Ngee Ann Student Toastmaster Club APR 2017 – APR 2019 - Assist Area Director in organizing events between different clubs. - Assist Vice-President of Education in planning chapter meetings and establishing long-term goals for the club. - Executive Planning Committee for Speech Craft Competition 2017. - Organization Committee for 4 Days 3 Nights annual camp.
